# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]
- Add support to use docker and docker compose to deploy the system
- Fix the input shape for the xception model 
- Include the custom models in the **poc** folder to the main mechanism


## [0.1.0]
### Added
- Include a mechanism to load pre-trained CNN models to identify the objects in the images
- Add a Rest API as entry point to the system using Flask
- Use Swagger to document the Rest API
- Include a POC script to test transfer learning to a custom CNN model for detecting specific objects
- Include a POC script to test some concepts related to Explainable Artificial Intelligence (XAI) 
